OL,3,CManx care services stabilise after
OL,4,Cextreme pressure as CEO announces
OL,5,Cdeparture
OL,7,FManx Care has confirmed that pressures
OL,8,Fon its services have begun to
OL,9,Fstabilise following a period of
OL,10,Fexceptional demand that saw the
OL,11,Forganisation escalate to the highest
OL,12,Flevel of operational pressure earlier
OL,13,Fthis week.
OL,15,FThe update comes as Chief Executive
OL,16,FTeresa Cope announced she will step
OL,17,Fdown this summer, after leading the
OL,18,FIsle of Man health service since its
OL,19,Finception.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
