PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778793068
OL,3,CManx care services stabilise after
OL,4,Cextreme pressure as CEO announces
OL,5,Cdeparture
OL,7,FManx Care was officially formed in
OL,8,FApril 2021, following recommendations
OL,9,Ffrom Sir Jonathan Michael's 2019
OL,10,Freview into the Island's healthcare
OL,11,Fsystem.
OL,13,FFollowing extreme pressures over the
OL,14,Flast 48 hours, Manx Care said services
OL,15,Fhave now transitioned from OPEL 4 to
OL,16,FOPEL 3 as demand becomes more
OL,17,Fmanageable. The organisation said
OL,18,Fwhile this indicates improvement,
OL,19,Fhospitals remain busy and capacity and
OL,20,Fpatient flow are being closely
OL,21,Fmonitored.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
