OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778793068
OL,3,CManx care services stabilise after
OL,4,Cextreme pressure as CEO announces
OL,5,Cdeparture
OL,7,FDuring the peak, a combination of very
OL,8,Fhigh adult bed occupancy, patients
OL,9,Fwaiting over 12 hours in the Emergency
OL,10,FDepartment, and a large number of
OL,11,Fpatients awaiting assessment forced
OL,12,FManx Care to take immediate action.
OL,14,FNineteen elective operations were
OL,15,Frescheduled, but the majority of
OL,16,Fplanned care has continued.
OL,18,FEfforts are now underway to restore
OL,19,Felective activity, with all affected
OL,20,Fpatients being contacted directly to
OL,21,Frebook their care.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
