OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778793068
OL,3,CManx care services stabilise after
OL,4,Cextreme pressure as CEO announces
OL,5,Cdeparture
OL,7,FThis is the second time in 18 months
OL,8,Fthat Manx Care has needed to redeploy
OL,9,Felective capacity to safeguard urgent
OL,10,Fand emergency care services.
OL,12,FThe declaration of OPEL 4 is a
OL,13,Fstructured and internationally
OL,14,Frecognised escalation process, only
OL,15,Fused when normal operations are no
OL,16,Flonger possible and immediate actions
OL,17,Fare required to protect patient safety.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
