FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778793068
OL,3,CManx care services stabilise after
OL,4,Cextreme pressure as CEO announces
OL,5,Cdeparture
OL,7,FManx Care's Interim Executive Director
OL,8,Fof Operations, Shaun Stacey, said "Our
OL,9,Fpriority at all times is to keep
OL,10,Fpatients safe and ensure those who
OL,11,Fneed urgent care are treated as
OL,12,Fquickly as possible.
OL,14,F"The past 48 hours have seen
OL,15,Fexceptional demand across our
OL,16,Fservices, and declaring OPEL 4 enabled
OL,17,Fus to take the necessary steps to
OL,18,Fmanage this safely.
OL,26,@pD@cOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
