CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778793068
OL,3,CManx care services stabilise after
OL,4,Cextreme pressure as CEO announces
OL,5,Cdeparture
OL,7,FWe recognise the impact that
OL,8,Frescheduling appointments can have,
OL,9,Fand we are contacting all affected
OL,10,Fpatients directly to rebook their care
OL,11,Fat the earliest opportunity."
OL,13,FPatients are encouraged to attend
OL,14,Fappointments as normal unless
OL,15,Fcontacted otherwise, and Manx Care
OL,16,Fsays ensuring safe, high-quality care
OL,17,Fremains its top priority.
OL,26,@sD@]O]
